    {
      "id": "declaration-walkthrough-step-1",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 1",
      "position": { "x": -260, "y": 40 },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 1: Identity + Dependencies\n\nOpen the declaration editor and set:\n- `identity.graphId`\n- `identity.name`\n- `identity.version`\n\nThen update `dependencies.nodeTypes` to include the primitives you intend to use.\n\nExpected:\n- [ ] Identity changes persist\n- [ ] Dependency warnings are sensible"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "declaration-walkthrough-step-2",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 2",
      "position": { "x": -260, "y": 330 },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 2: Mutation Policy\n\nToggle:\n- `authority.mutation.appendOnly`\n\nExpected:\n- [ ] Edit affordances match policy (updates should be constrained when appendOnly is true)\n- [ ] No unexpected crashes or blank panels"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "declaration-walkthrough-step-3",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 3",
      "position": { "x": -260, "y": 620 },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 3: Export Surfaces\n\nAdd an export surface under:\n- `declaration.surfaces[]`\n\nUse it to define allowlists for:\n- views\n- node classes / edge classes\n- scripts\n- declarations\n\nExpected:\n- [ ] Surface edits persist\n- [ ] Downstream bridge exposure uses the surface policy (when configured)"
      }
    },
